#### Performance Considerations

- Match concurrency model to bottleneck (I/O vs CPU).
- Process spawn overhead—pool reuse essential.
- Oversubscription causes context switch thrashing.

#### Best Practices

- Profile before parallelizing.
- Prefer asyncio for I/O-heavy; processes for CPU-heavy.
- Avoid shared mutable state across threads/processes.
- Use structured concurrency patterns.

#### Real-world Industry Use Cases

- **Web crawlers:** Async fetch + process pool parse.
- **Video platforms:** Parallel transcoding farms (processes).
- **Analytics ETL:** Concurrent I/O, parallel transforms.

