- C extensions may change calculus—profile.

#### Best Practices

- Know your workload type before choosing concurrency model.
- Don't assume threads parallelize Python CPU code.
- Monitor and benchmark, don't guess GIL impact.
- Follow nogil ecosystem if adopting free-threaded Python.

#### Real-world Industry Use Cases

- **Instagram:** Threading for I/O + multiprocessing historically.
- **NumPy/scipy:** C-level GIL release for compute.
- **ML inference:** GPU/C extensions sidestep GIL for compute.

